','Vipps/MobilePay Recurring Payments requires WooCommerce Subscriptions to be installed and active. You can purchase and download %s here.'=>'Vipps/MobilePay Faste Betalinger kræver, at WooCommerce Subscriptions er installeret og aktivt. Du kan købe og downloade %s her.','Vipps/MobilePay Recurring Payments works by redirecting your customers to the Vipps MobilePay portal for confirmation. It creates a payment plan and charges your users on the intervals you specify.'=>'Vipps/MobilePay Faste Betalinger fungerer ved at omdirigere dine kunder til Vipps MobilePay-portalen til bekræftelse. Den opretter en betalingsplan og opkræver dine brugere med de intervaller, du angiver.','Waiting for you to capture the payment'=>'Venter på, at du trække beløpet.','We hit Vipps/MobilePay\'s rate limit, we will retry later.'=>'Vi har ramt Vipps/MobilePays rategrænse, vi vil forsøge igen senere.','When a renewal order happens we have to wait a few days for the money to be drawn from the customer. This settings controls the status to give these renewal orders before the charge completes.'=>'Når en fornyelsesordre finder sted, skal vi vente et par dage, inden pengene trækkes fra kunden. Denne indstilling styrer statussen for at give disse fornyelsesordrer, inden betalingen er fuldført.','Where we should source the agreement description from. Displayed in the Vipps/MobilePay app.'=>'Hvor vi skal hente aftalebeskrivelsen fra. Vises i Vipps/MobilePay-appen.','Yes'=>'Ja','You can not partially refund a pending or due charge. Please wait till the payment clears first or refund the full amount instead.'=>'Du kan ikke delvist refundere en afventende eller forfalden betaling. Vent venligst, indtil betalingen er gennemført, eller refundér i stedet det fulde beløb.','You cannot refund a charge that was made more than 365 days ago. This order was created %s days ago.'=>'Du kan ikke refundere en betaling, der blev foretaget for mere end 365 dage siden. Denne ordre blev oprettet for %s dage siden.','Your Vipps/MobilePay Recurring Payments gateway is not correctly configured.'=>'Din Vipps/MobilePay Faste Betalinger gateway er ikke korrekt konfigureret.','Your WordPress URL is not passing Merchant Agreement URL validation. Is your website publicly accessible?'=>'Din WordPress URL passer ikke Merchant Agreement URL-validering. Er din hjemmeside offentligt tilgængelig?']];
